A. Mission Description and Budget Item Justification
This program is initiated in FY 2026. Research and develop solutions to Damage Control and Firefighting issues to include developing environmentally friendly and
effective alternatives to existing firefighting systems. This program funds critical efforts in shipboard fire detection/suppression systems, fire prevention features, damage
control, personnel protection, and advanced firefighting equipment.

