-Conduct NPES level test and evaluation of cyber hardening measures in a land based test environment.
-Update GFI required for delivery to the shipbuilder for any power, weight, cooling or cabling changes required
by the shipbuilder to evaluate emerging new NPES architectures.
FY 2027 Base Plans:
