 common services within SWFTS.

 FY25 continues funding for development of TI-26 and completion of TI-24. Cybersecurity efforts continue to evolve in future baselines to keep pace with the threat.
 Integration efforts for additional submarine payloads including MK48 ADCAP variants APB 6, APB 7 and APB 8.

