D. Acquisition Strategy
The Single Acquisition Management Plan (SAMP) for the ISIS Program TI-20/22/24 with Mast is approved 07 Jul 2017. The Program Streamlined Acquisition Plan with
Services (PSTRAP-M) for ISIS TI-26/28/30 is approved 08 Mar 2024. The Acquisition Program Baseline Agreement (APBA) for ISIS Program TI-26 Increment with
APB-25 & APB-27 is approved 01 May 2024. The ISIS will provide mission critical, all weather, visual, and electronic search, digital image management, indication,
warning, and platform architecture interface capabilities for SSN 688, SSN 21, SSN 774, SSN 826 and SSGN class submarines.




