 the MyNavy HR Transformation Program that includes yet expands beyond the RRL core initiatives identified above. In support of the broader MyNavy HR enterprise,
 the LS will provide a centralized, authoritative repository for Interactive Multimedia Instruction (IMI) courseware, officer and citizen development (NJROTC and ROTC
 candidate management), enlisted advancement exam development and distribution, enlisted degree completions, and tuition assistance authorizations.
