D. Acquisition Strategy
On 30 March 2017, the DAB reviewed the CH-53K program for a MS C decision allowing entry into Production and the ADM was signed by USD AT&L on 4 April 2017
resulting in an ACAT 1C designation. Initial Operational Test & Evaluation (IOT&E) completed April 2022; Initial Operating Capability (IOC) achieved in May 2022; and
Full Rate Production (FRP) approved in December 2022.




