Crypto Mod, ACC 2.x, SATURN ed. 5 and MUOS 4.x. Execute Gen5B Crypto Modernization 2, SINCGARS 3.2.
Continue Gen6 Crypto Mod 2 Quantum Resilience (QR). Attain Gen5 NSA and Gen5 JITC Certification. Deliver
Gen5 Ver 009 Release.
