       and increase survivability.

       Increase of $5.609 million for Marine Aviation supporting MV-22 investment to REVAMP, NAGC Proliferated Low Earth Orbit (pLEO) Beyond Line of Sight
       (BLOS).

       Increase of $40.551 million for Marine Aviation investment for DI/MANGL to increase crypto security of architectures, enabling connection to tactical clouds at the
       edge.

